Class PolyRegContent

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.knime.base.node.mine.regression.RegressionContent
      • org.knime.base.node.mine.regression.polynomial.learner2.PolyRegContent

  • final class PolyRegContent
extends RegressionContent
    Utility class that stores results of linear regression models. It is used by the learner node model and the predictor node model.
    Since:
    2.10
    Author:
    Heiko Hofer

        Create new instance.
        Parameters:
        outSpec - the spec of the output
        valueCount - the number of data values in the training data set
        factorList - the factors (nominal parameters)
        covariateList - the covariates (numeric parameters)
        beta - the estimated regression factors
        offsetValue - offset value (a user defined intercept)
        covMat - the covariance matrix
        rSquared - the r-square value
        adjustedRSquared - the adjusted r-quare value
        stats - summary statistics of the parameters (for all powers)
        maxExponent - The maximal exponent in the model.
